snippet.title: Golden Idol Investigations: The Sins of New Wells | Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOW!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3333870/Golden_Idol_Investigations__The_Sins_of_New_Wells/
Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/the-rise-of-the-golden-idol-switch/
PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10010047
Xbox: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/the-rise-of-the-golden-idol/9nhqgsh0598d

Sinners, drugs, murder and journalists run rampant in the city of New Wells. Homicide detective Roy Samson has been transferred to the 9th District to unravel the corrupt underground network of the city.
